shutter ( thai : ชัตเตอร์ กดติดวิญญาณ ) is a 2004 thai horror film by banjong pisanthanakun and parkpoom wongpoom ; starring ananda everingham , natthaweeranuch thongmee , and achita sikamana .   it focuses on mysterious images seen in developed pictures .   the film was a huge box office success making it one of the best horror movies of thailand recognized worldwide .   the film was remade in 2008 under the same title .